## Required Reading

Before any task, read the relevant documentation:

| Doc | Format | When to Read |
|-----|--------|--------------|
| `docs/TODO.md` | Markdown | Check first - active tasks |
| `docs/api.yaml` | YAML | Before API changes |
| `docs/schema.yaml` | YAML | Before database changes |
| `docs/FILE_FORMATS.md` | Markdown | Understanding doc formats |

### File Format Guidelines

Use token-efficient formats for AI documentation:

| Format | Use For | Token Efficiency |
|--------|---------|------------------|
| **YAML** | Schemas, APIs, configs | Most efficient |
| **Markdown** | Docs, guides, changelogs | Good (headings aid navigation) |
| **XML** | Constraints, rules (Claude-optimized) | Good for distinct sections |
| **JSON** | Avoid for large files | Least efficient |

---

## Key Directories

```
src/app/          # Next.js pages
src/app/api/      # API routes
src/components/   # React components
src/lib/          # Utilities
docs/             # Documentation
```

---

## Critical Rules

### [Category 1 - e.g., Authentication]

```typescript
// ALWAYS do this
import { checkAuth } from '@/lib/auth'

// NEVER do this
// Don't trust client-side auth state
```

### [Category 2 - e.g., Database]

```typescript
// Use server client for mutations
import { createServerClient } from '@/lib/db/server'
```

---

## Running the App

```bash
# Development
npm run dev

# Production build
npm run build && npm start

# With Docker
docker compose up -d
```

